title: 'pallet-staking-async: gate reap_stash and withdraw_unbonded kill by existential deposit'
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: "Gated `reap_stash` strictly by ED and not by `min(MinValidatorBond,\
    \ MinNominatorBond).max(ED)`. Apply the same fix for `withdraw_unbonded` to kill stash if ledger.active < ED.\r\n"
crates:
- name: pallet-staking-async
  bump: patch
